column5: Thanks to Handlebarz for my first Muskie. I was throwing a Double 10 in Gold on Gold and nailed this beauty 42"er off of a rock ledge. Trout Lake in North Bay.
Nice catch there Blair. I see you got the Dale Jr look going on there,LOL
